aiting on for a few years now.\u0026nbsp; The square headlights have been discontined for many years as a new part.\u0026nbsp; On top of that the original DOT approved lights that were stock on all later model Vanagon here in the USA were made to diffuse light.\u0026nbsp; This was supposed to help not blind on coming traffic, but it made your lights from the driver\u0026#39;s stand point, dim and unfocused.\u0026nbsp; However in Europe they were fine with an H4 housing that had brighter bulbs available and also focused the light so the driver could actually see better (what a concept).\u0026nbsp; These were considered the best headlights you could get for your late model Vanagon.\u0026nbsp; However since the square headlight in Europe was actually rare, these were always had to come by.\u0026nbsp; Fast forward to now, we have been working with a supplier to reproduce the great H4 square lights and we are finally ready to start selling these as a full kit.\u0026nbsp; \u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ciframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uxOvQmR6DMQ\" width=\"560\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"46:[\"$\",\"div\",\"12252\",{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"className\":\"rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow group relative h-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/40\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative bg-muted aspect-square\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"href\":\"/products/vanagon-h4-square-headlight-kit-with-led-bulbs\",\"className\":\"absolute inset-0 z-0\",\"aria-label\":\"View Vanagon H4 Square Headlight Kit with LED bulbs\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L40\",null,{\"src\":\"https://ph3ar-vercel.s3.amazonaws.com/products